Fred Theodore A. Shlapak

Age : 72Public asset : 7,500 USDLinked companies :  ViXS Systems Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Fred T. Shlapak is Chairman at SiGe Semiconductor, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at ViXS Systems, Inc. Mr. Shlapak was previously employed as an Independent Director by Applied Micro Circuits Corp., President & CEO-Semiconductor Products by Motorola Corp., and President-Semiconductor Products Sector by Motorola, Inc.He also served on the board at Tundra Semiconductor Corp. and Gennum Corp.He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Waterloo and a graduate degree from The University of Waterloo.



